name: jacked
content:
Add to word list
Add to word list
having strong, well-developed muscles, especially as a result of working out (= exercising in order to improve the strength or appearance of your body): He was trying to get himself jacked for the photoshoot. These female weightlifters are absolutely jacked.
More examplesFewer examplesWhen he got out of prison he was jacked. Do you want to be so jacked that your biceps are tearing your sleeves? There's a reason the top bodybuilders are more jacked than the top powerlifters.
